Add an Image Widget to Display Graphics in the Dashboard

To include company logos, icons, or graphics in the dashboard, drag the image widget to the canvas, click Image inside the image widget, and upload a new image or select one from the Gallery tab. The image file must be no more than 2 GB.

Required user permissions: Create CRM Analytics Applications and Create and Edit CRM Analytics Dashboards. Chatter must also be enabled in the org. 

The image widget supports .svg, .png, jpeg, .jpg, .gif, and .bmp file types. To overlay one image on top of another, place an image widget inside a container widget.
